sentences.sContent: The answer presumable is gonna be that the best version of the personality theory doesn't require item for item, having the very same believes, memories, desires and so forth.
sentences.sContent_eng: The answer presumable is gonna be that the best version of the personality theory doesn't require item for item, having the very same believes, memories, desires and so forth.
sentences.sCn: 可以揣测到的答案是,人格论最好的版本是,不去要求一丝不变，不要求,完全一样的信仰，记忆，渴望等等。

trans.tranOther: able to be presumed or taken for granted
